creases the user\'s max HP for the remainder<br>of the quest and increases the entire team\'s<br>strength and critical rate. If this skill is used<br>when the user is in high power mode,<br>a variant called Smithy Arm: Power Mode will<br>be used instead.<br>Smithy Arm: Power Mode Deals damage to<br>the target and nearby enemies, dispels one<br>buff from each of them, and immediately<br>readies the user\'s initial skill, displayed at<br>the top of their skill list, for use.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Skill Energy Required: 7,475<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbHP +3%<br>\\u30fbStrength +15%<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 15 seconds<br>\\u30fbCritical Rate +10%<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 15 seconds<br><br><color=#00008B>High Power Mode:<\/color><br>Damage: 450 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Damage: 1,660 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Skill Energy Required: 7,475<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbDispels Buffs<br><\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/dffb0cc210e6ca60f7b0ec47d24543562.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Defense +15%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIncreases defense by 15%.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Chain Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/87595b7438e74e5502d8b830d6bd16832.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>(Water) Frostbite = User Strength +13%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIf a team member is attuned to Water:<br>increases their strength by 13% for 15 seconds<br>when they successfully inflict an enemy with<br>frostbite. After activating, this ability will not<br>activate again for 10 seconds.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n<div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/45e56814cd3c293c83f5513d3dc5800b2.png\\"><\/span><span>Mechanized Blacksmith<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Increases damage to frostbitten enemies by 30%.<br>In addition, using a skill will grant the user a<br>strength amp with a maximum team amp level<br>of two. After this amp is granted, this ability will<br>not grant it again for 30 seconds.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/c0b3ec2bdf2af0f73ef2627b87da47152.png\\"><\/span><span>Potent Burn Res +100%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to burning by 100%.<br>When the user is hit by an attack that would have<br>inflicted burning on them, their strength is increased<br>by 15% for 10 seconds. After activating, this buff will<br>not activate again for 15 seconds.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/e7eed50a5972abee7f228825cdf9960e2.png\\"><\/span><span>HP 70% = Skill Damage & Flame Res I<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>When HP is 70% or above, increases attack<br>skill damage by 35% and adds 10% to flame<br>resistance.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. The stats shown here represent the adventurer at level 100 with 70 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div>2. The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities.<\/div><div>3. The stats for the adventurer included in this notification shown in any prior notifications or preview videos were the stats at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div>4. When an adventurer&#39;s skill level increases, the skill gauge will fill more slowly when set as a shared skill.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1632204000,"prev_article_id":"2461","next_article_id":"2485","image_path":"","update_time":1631687429}}}'